# ── PROJECT LAYER — never lives in the seed ──────────────────────────────────
# These directories belong to project forks. The seed has them empty (.gitkeep).
# Merging upstream/main into a project fork will NEVER touch these paths.

# Tenant storage — data files stay out of the seed repo.
# In a project fork, all storage/ is yours to commit freely.
storage/*
!storage/.gitkeep

# Project-specific custom blocks built with AI
# Exception: _TEMPLATE.tsx is part of the seed (shows the pattern to follow)
src/components/specialized/
!src/components/specialized/_TEMPLATE.tsx

# local Claude Code settings (machine-specific, never committed)
.claude/

.vercel
.env*.local
/.history/
